---
import Icon from "./Icon.astro";
---

<section class="box skills github-stats-container">
  <h2>About Me</h2>
  <p>
    I really enjoy using my interest in development to build a satisfying
    career. I love learning, coming up with new ideas, and improving my skills
    in open-source work. This website displays the projects I've worked on and
    the skills I've developed, with the goal of making software that's both
    efficient and looks good, providing users with a smooth experience. <br><br> I focus
    on both front-end and back-end development, customizing solutions to fit
    each project's specific needs. Whether you're a client, a fellow developer,
    or just curious, take a look at my portfolio and reach out if you'd like to
    collaborate. Thanks for stopping by, and let's make some amazing digital
    experiences together!
  </p>
</section>

<style>
  .github-stats-container {
    position: relative;
    background: var(--github-show-box-background-skills-color);

    border-radius: 0.75rem;
  }

  .github-stats-container::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: -1px;
    left: -1px;
    right: -1px;
    bottom: -1px;
    background: linear-gradient(105deg, #ffd800, #ff5520, #750cf2, #0cbcf2);
    z-index: -1;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
  }
  .github-stats-container::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(75deg, #ffd800, #ff5520, #750cf2, #0cbcf2);
    z-index: -2;
    filter: blur(10px);
    border-radius: 0.85rem;
  }

  .box {
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.5rem;

    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }

  .moved-word::first-word {
    float: left;
    margin-right: 5px; /* Adjust the spacing as needed */
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  .skills h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .skills p {
    color: var(--gray-400);
  }
  .skills {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 50em) {
    .box {
      border-radius: 0.75rem;
      padding: 2.5rem;
    }

    .skills {
      display: grid;
      font-size: 20px;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .skills h2 {
      font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    }
  }

  /* =========================================================== */
</style>
